---
title: Spiced Cauliflower & Freekeh Salad with Roasted Kumara & Toasted Almonds
description: This delightful dish is a celebration of wholesome roasted veggies with freekeh and toasted almonds. Add Souk Market spices for
extra flavour, then top it off with crumbly Greek-style cheese.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-cauliflower-freekeh-salad-a55637eb.jpg
